SIMPLE: overmeasure
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overmeasure
<hw>O`ver*meas"ure</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To measure
or estimate too largely.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overmeasure</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Overmeasure
<hw>O"ver*meas`ure</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Excessive
measure; the excess beyond true or proper measure; surplus.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overmeddle</ent>⟦br⟧
